## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of Stone Age life. Additionally, the lack of written records from the Stone Age means that much of the understanding is based on archaeological findings and interpretations, which can vary. The time span of the Stone Age also means that experiences could differ significantly across different periods and regions.